<doc id="740055" wikidata="Q1256977" url="?curid=740055" title="3 (disambiguation)">
<text>[[3]] is a number, numeral, and glyph.

3, three, or III may also refer to:

* AD 3, the third year of the AD era
* 3 BC, the third year before the AD era
* March, the third month
==Books==
* &quot;3&quot;, a 2004 novel by Julie Hilden 
