* &quot;Three&quot; (comics), a graphic novel by Kieron Gillen
* &quot;Three&quot; (novel), a 2003 suspense novel by Ted Dekker
* &quot;Three By Flannery O&#x27;Connor&quot;, collection Flannery O&#x27;Connor bibliography
